<figureCitation box="[326,427,1793,1819]" captionStart="FIGURES 218 – 227" captionStartId="45.[264,370,1584,1605]" captionTargetBox="[370,1238,321,1548]" captionTargetId="figure@45.[358,1274,319,1557]" captionTargetPageId="45" captionText="FIGURES 218 – 227. Scaphoideus zhangi sp. nov. 218. Male genital capsule, lateral view; 219. Dorsal pygophore process; 220. Subgenital plate and style; 221. Style; 222. Apophysis of style; 223. Connective and paraphyses, ventral view; 224. Connective, paraphysis and aedeagus, lateral view; 225. Aedeagus, caudal view; 226. Front wing; 227. Female ovipositor. Scale line indicates 0.1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/169118/files/figure.png" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
